## Roadmap: expanding play styles

Progressive rollout — do not add modes to every level at once.

| Step | What | Why |
|------|------|-----|
| **5** ✅ | `stageOrder` / `stageSlot` shuffle | Replayability without new content |
| **6** | `activePool` per level — shuffle a **subset** of indices | Keeps run length sane as roster grows |
| **7** | Add 1–2 Tier B modes into Level 4+ pools only | Fresh content for veterans, gentle onboarding |
| — | Mode-select / practice screen | Deferred until players ask |

### Step 5 — shipped: random mode order per level

At the **start of each level**, shuffle all `GAME_SHAPES` indices once. Play each mode exactly once in that random order. Reshuffle on next level.

- State: `stageOrder: number[]`, `stageSlot: number`
- Derived: `shapeIndex = stageOrder[stageSlot]`
- Persist in `ISavedGame`; old saves migrate to sequential order + slot from `shapeIndex`
- Stars key unchanged: `stars_L${level}_S${shapeIndex}`

**Files:** `useCandyBreak.ts`

### Step 6 — pending: level-gated `activePool`

Replace "always shuffle all N modes" with a **pool per level** that grows as the player advances.

| Level | Pool tier | Stages per level (target) |
|-------|-----------|---------------------------|
| 1–2 | Core only | 5 |
| 3–4 | Core + Mid | 7 |
| 5 | Core + Mid + Advanced (+ Tier B when shipped) | 8–10 |

**Core:** `classic`, `color-target`, `locked-tiles`, `bomb-storm`  
**Mid:** `timer-attack`, `move-saver`, `pure-match`  
**Advanced:** `multiplier-rush`, `order-collect`, `combo-goal`

Implementation sketch:

- `getActivePool(level: number): number[]` — returns eligible shape indices
- `createStageOrder(pool)` — already accepts optional pool; pass `getActivePool(level)`
- Unlock is implicit via level — no score gate, no mode-select UI
- Persist `activePool` in save or re-derive from `level` on resume

**Files:** `useCandyBreak.ts`, optionally `src/constants/game.ts` for pool tiers

### Step 7 — pending: Tier B modes (Level 4+ only)

Add after Step 6 so new modes do not bloat early levels.

**Candidates:** `jelly-tiles`, `stone-blocks`, `special-hunt`  
**Tier C (later):** `color-flood`, `ice-spread`, `mystery`

Per-mode checklist (same as candy-break rule):

1. `src/types/index.ts` — `PlayStyle`, optional `IGameShape` fields
2. `src/constants/game.ts` — append to `GAME_SHAPES` + pool tier constant
3. `src/hooks/useCandyBreak.ts` — `SHAPE_GOALS`, `initializeStage`, goal/finalize logic, save/restore
4. `App.tsx` — banner + fourth HUD card if needed
5. `src/i18n/translations.ts` — ko/en strings

## Architecture (i18n)

| Layer | Path | Responsibility |
|-------|------|----------------|
| Types | `src/i18n/types.ts` | `Language`, `IStrings`, banner keys |
| Strings | `src/i18n/translations.ts` | ko/en copy for all UI text |
| Format | `src/i18n/format.ts` | `{placeholder}` interpolation |
| Context | `src/i18n/I18nContext.tsx` | `I18nProvider`, `useI18n`, AsyncStorage `appLanguage` |
| Toggle | `src/components/LanguageToggle.tsx` | KO/EN switch (intro screen only) |

- Language choice persists in `AsyncStorage` key `appLanguage` (`ko` | `en`, default `ko`)
- `App.tsx` wraps content in `I18nProvider`; intro sets language, game screens read it
- Add new UI strings to **both** `ko` and `en` in `translations.ts`; use `format()` for dynamic values

## Shipped fixes

### Bomb / lightning flash

`bombActivating: IPosition | null` — UI treats a cell as bomb if `bombPosition` **or** `bombActivating` matches.

**Files:** `useCandyBreak.ts`, `App.tsx`

### Immediate goal update

`goalRemaining` updates per cascade step via `computeGoalAfterSteps`, not only in `finalizeMove`.

**Files:** `useCandyBreak.ts`

### Game Over overlay

- Full-board dim + card panel for readable text
- Tap overlay → `restart()` (retry stage) or `restartFromLevelOne()` (full win)

**Files:** `App.tsx`

### Locked-tiles touch

- Frozen cells use `Pressable`; tapping frozen no longer clears adjacent selection

**Files:** `App.tsx`, `useCandyBreak.ts`

## Play styles (current — 10 modes)

| Style | Goal | Moves | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|-------|
| `classic` | Clear N candies | Limited | Bomb at 60% moves left |
| `color-target` | Clear N of `targetColor` | Limited | Random target on init |
| `locked-tiles` | Thaw all frozen cells | Limited | 2 hits to thaw |
| `multiplier-rush` | Score threshold | Limited | Combo doubles multiplier (max 8×) |
| `bomb-storm` | Clear N candies | Limited | Bomb at 30% moves; respawns |
| `timer-attack` | Clear N candies | Unlimited | 90s countdown |
| `order-collect` | Clear N per color in sequence | Limited | Shuffled Red/Blue/Gold queue |
| `combo-goal` | Reach N cascade steps | Limited | Only step 2+ counts |
| `move-saver` | Clear N candies | Limited | 2+ cascade refunds 1 move (max 3/stage) |
| `pure-match` | Clear N candies | Limited | No striped/rainbow |

